================================================================================
Third-Party Components
================================================================================

This software uses the following third-party libraries. Full license texts
are available in the Software Bill of Materials (SBOM) generated during the
release process.

Rust Dependencies:
- libloading (ISC) - Dynamic library loading
- ndarray (MIT/Apache-2.0) - N-dimensional arrays
- pyo3 (MIT/Apache-2.0) - Python bindings for Rust
- serde (MIT/Apache-2.0) - Serialization framework
- serde_json (MIT/Apache-2.0) - JSON support for serde
- zip (MIT) - ZIP archive support
- log (MIT/Apache-2.0) - Logging facade
- image (MIT/Apache-2.0) - Image processing

Python Dependencies:
- numpy (BSD-3-Clause) - Numerical computing
- maturin (MIT/Apache-2.0) - Build backend for PyO3

For a complete list of dependencies and their licenses, see the SBOM
artifact published with each release.

